detail.name: Nappa
detail.effect: [On Play] If you placed a card from your energy into its owner's Drop during this turn, choose up to 1 [Field] with a cost of 2 or less in your opponent's Battle Area and place it into its owner's Drop.

detail.name: ナッパ
detail.effect: 【登場時】このターン中、自分のエナジーがドロップに置かれていた場合、相手のバトルエリアのコスト2以下の【フィールド】1枚までを選び、ドロップに置く。
